window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Adryan </b></p> <p>I was ruthless, brutal. A sociopath by all accounts. The leader of the American Vampire Clan, a male who all feared because I was merciless.</p> <p>And then I found my mate. Kayla. So fragile. Breakable. So human.</p> <p>I’d make her mine, and she’d hate me for it. I wanted to give her pain with pleasure, wanted to break her skin and lick up the blood I spilled...take Kayla into me like she’d take me into her.</p> <p>I’d have her surrendering to my needs. I’d give her my body but wouldn't be able to give her my heart.</p> <p>How could I when it wasn’t something I had to offer, when I was nothing but a coldhearted killer?</p> <p>So when the threats come to my front door, it’s time to show my female she’s mated to the most dangerous vampire in the world.</p>"; 
